Hey! Now we update our app with a new design and a range of improvements, how about:

* See delivery price and compare between restaurant already in the restaurant list
* Sort by delivery price and distance
* See the restaurant's comments in the user reviews
* Possibility to make a pre-order - choose the desired delivery time!

Not bad, huh?

Hey! Now we update our app again with a range of improvements:

* Restaurants that offer student discounts are clearly displayed
* Student discounts are automatically active for logged in users
* Logged in users can view their previous orders
* Logged in users can easily re-order a previous order

Moreover, this version is both faster and more stable.

Thanks alot for using OnlinePizza!

In this version, we have fine-tuned the design a little bit so it will be even more fun to order food. Since the previous version, the app also includes a number of improvements for all logged in users, such as:
* To view their previous orders
* Get the student discount enabled automatically
* The ability to reorder the favorite food - in a few clicks

Have a nice summer! And you, thank you for using OnlinePizza!

In this version we have increased the clarity of menus and carts and made it super easy to multiply products. You who are logged in can also view your latest orders and order again with just a few clicks - directly from the start page

We are also constantly working to improve performance so that the app will be as fast, stable and smooth as possible.

So, you have nothing to lose to download the latest version of the app, regardless of whether you are using the latest iPhone model or not.
